{"tid":451604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話時話，基本法/聯合聲明邊忽講過乜鳩'全面管冶權'","createTime":"2017-10-29T11:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T14:20:10.000Z","uid":48083,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"47373569b264bc19dd785df34cc2fcd3f985a6dc","tid":451604,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:29:43.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係主權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除外交軍事外香港人自己搞掂<br />\n<br />\n仲有係'高度自治'，指一種狀態<br />\n<br />\n唔係'高度自治權'<br />\n<br />\n同中国人講合約精神真係嘥鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803a9785a7a9d5e27319485d73b305e4ce262d47","tid":451604,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:30:37.000Z","msg":"無限釋法。"},{"pid":"1eca45061b8c5310c6df1c5743d61663b1cd6d9c","tid":451604,"uid":4964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:32:28.000Z","msg":"解釋權=玩晒<br />\n人大有日出嚟解釋話香港人唔食屎就係違反基本法第一條都仲得"},{"pid":"efc4b26b0cbf4ef6b8815745a16d5c44c9b73e7f","tid":451604,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:33:25.000Z","msg":"佢話唔知第幾條其實已經講左 你咬佢食咩 第一日識共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35dbaaf98743804f1d3ba782998d4d2ad1426353","tid":451604,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:40:34.000Z","msg":"老鼠成：<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯鄧小平並不承諾中央在任何情況下都不會干預，反指出「有些干預是必要的」。中央在必要時有干預的責任和權力，因為中央對香港有管治權。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">在簽署中英聯合聲明之前，</span>中國政府已清楚表明，主權和治權分不開；在恢復行使對香港的主權的時候，中央便擁有對香港的全面管治權。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/新聞/追溯初心-100487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?